    <section id="faq">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- <div class="row"> -->
                <h1>FAQ.</h1>
                <div class="faq">
                    <h3 id="faq-heading">The server list is not showing up!</h3>
                    <p>Try restarting BeamMP as this can sometimes happen, if this fails to fix your issue please create a post on the <a href="https://forum.beammp.com/">forum</a></p>
                    <h3 id="faq-heading">Help! Im getting error codes</h3>
                    <p>All errors codes meaning can be found on our <a href="https://wiki.beammp.com/en/error-codes">wiki</a>, if you need further help you can create a post on the <a href="https://forum.beammp.com/">forum</a>.</p>
                    <h3 id="faq-heading"> Does this work with pirated versions of BeamNG.drive?</h3>
                    <p>We don’t know if it works with pirated versions of BeamNG.drive, but we <b>will not</b> provide any support to non legit copies of the game.</p>
                    <h3 id="faq-heading">How do I host a server?</h3>
                    <p>Hosting a server is very easy! To do this simply head on <a href="https://wiki.beammp.com/en/home/server-installation">this page</a> of our wiki and follow all the instructions.</p>
                    <h3 id="faq-heading">Can I use mods?</h3>
                    <p>Mods are supported in the new version v2.0. These are installed on the server. See our <a href="https://wiki.beammp.com/en/home/server-installation">wiki</a> for more infomation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
